----------------------------------------- 10.5 WHAT IS ENTROPY? --------------------------------------

IN NATURE THERE IS A TENDANCY TO CHANGE TO A STATE OF LOWER ENERGY (LOWER ENTHALPY)

HOWEVER, SOMETIMES ENDOTHERMIC REACTIONS CAN BE SPONTANEOUS TOO.

IN NATURE, THERE IS A TENDANCY TO CHANGE TO A STATE OF GREATER DISORDER

ENTROPY:
	A STATE OF MORE CHAOS

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

CHANGES TOWARD GREATER ENTROPY:
	SOLID PHASE --> LIQUID PHASE --> GAS PHASE

	COMPOUND --> ELEMENTS

